Package org.codehaus.mojo.versions

Class DynamicVersioningSCMPlugin

java.lang.Object
org.apache.maven.plugin.AbstractMojo
org.codehaus.mojo.versions.DynamicVersioningSCMPlugin
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.apache.maven.plugin.ContextEnabled, org.apache.maven.plugin.Mojo
@Mojo(name="use-dynamic-version-from-scm", defaultPhase=INITIALIZE) public class DynamicVersioningSCMPlugin extends org.apache.maven.plugin.AbstractMojo
Maven plugin that uses SCM/VCS to enable dynamic versioning based on your version control system. Goal will set the version in a property.
Since:
2.17.0
Author:
Jimisola Laursen
